EDPPM Route Planner v1.3

The EDPPM Route Planner is a companion tool to EDPPM (Elite Dangerous PowerPlay Monitor) designed to calculate and visualize efficient travel routes between multiple star systems in Elite Dangerous.

Its primary goal is to reduce total travel distance when visiting many systems by applying Traveling Salesman Problem (TSP) techniques, while remaining responsive for large system lists.

ğŸ§­ Purpose

Minimize total jump distance across many systems

Avoid inefficient zig-zag routing

Provide a clear visual and textual route order

Support PowerPlay, BGS, and logistics planning

This tool is offline-first and operates on locally stored system data.

